                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480918-name-476" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-476" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-476" type="surname" value="WILKIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-476" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD WILKIS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 113). On 16th Sept., about half-past five o'clock in the morning, I saw the prisoners running in Brownlow-street, Bethnal-green—each had something in his hand—I ran after them, but could not catch them—John dropped a basket—I picked it up—it had this fowl in it (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—I took him next morning, at his father's, and found a dead fowl in the yard.</p>
